  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1, \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd ; \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bb5 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc2\u0b95\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Strong winds, rough seas; Warning to marine and fishing communities",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, the prevailing wind conditions will further increase in the western and southern coasts and the southern part of the country due to the southwest monsoon.",
        "The Upper and North-Western Provinces and Galle and Matara Districts are likely to witness several spells of rain.",
        "Uva and Eastern Provinces and Ambantota District are likely to experience rain or thundershowers in the afternoon or night at many places.",
        "Occasional gusty winds of 50-60 kmph may occur over western slopes of central hills, western and southern provinces.",
        "The public is advised to take adequate precautions during thunderstorms to minimize damage caused by temporary strong winds and lightning strikes.",
        "Due to the active position of Southwest Monsoon, occasional strong winds are likely to occur over western and southern seas for the next few days.",
        "Occasional rain or thundershowers are possible over coastal areas from Puttalam through Colombo and Galle to Ambantota.",
        "Winds will be from west to south-west and the wind speed will be (30-40) km/h from Colombo Ambantota through Galle and the wind speed may increase to (60-70) km/h in offshore areas.",
        "Wind speed may increase to (50-60) km/h over coastal areas from Puttalam to Colombo and Hambantota to Pottuvil.",
        "The seas offshore from Colombo Ambantota through Galle are very rough.",
        "The seas from Puttalam to Colombo and from Hambantota to Pottuvil are turbulent. Other seas surrounding the country are moderate.",
        "Sea waves (about 2.5 \u2013 3.0 m) are likely to increase in the coastal areas from Puttalam to Pottu through Colombo, Galle and Ambantota.",
        "From Puttalam through Colombo and Galle to Matara, there is a possibility of high waves in the coastal areas close to the coast.",
        "Therefore, the coastal areas from Colombo via Galle to Ambantota have been advised not to engage in fishing and naval activities within the next 24 hours."
      ],
